HEADWORD: Majusculae
<hw>Ma*jus"cu*lae</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos> <ety>[L.,
fem. pl. fr. <ets>majusculus</ets> somewhat greater or great, dim. of
